org.batfish.grammar.flatjuniper

Interface FlatJuniperParserListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplyGroupsApplicator, ApplyPathApplicator, ConfigurationBuilder, DeactivatedLinePruner, DeactivateLinePruner, DeactivateTreeBuilder, FlatJuniperParserBaseListener, GroupPruner, GroupTreeBuilder, InitialTreeBuilder, WildcardApplicator, WildcardPruner

    public interface FlatJuniperParserListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by FlatJuniperParser.
